{"tid":2227673,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會黃國健：泛民留任默認人大權力　胡志偉斥倒果為因","createTime":"2020-10-03T03:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T13:16:20.000Z","uid":80481,"like":60,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"63d1f5526bedd1312c9079f7d44613ad6fd74d50","tid":2227673,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T03:42:14.000Z","msg":"決定民主派去留的民調日前出爐，在兩者的支持者均不過半的情況下，19名議員決定留任延任一年的立法會。工聯會立法會議員黃國健今早（3日）於電台節目上表示，民主派留任代表默認了人大常委的決定能夠超越《基本法》，有此先例下日後人大再作任何凌駕《基本法》的決定，民主派的爭辯能力會減弱。<br />\n<br />\n決定留任的民主黨主席胡志偉反駁稱，人大能釋法是法律制度的先天局限，強調民主派對中央不斷扭曲《基本法》不能接受，批黃國健的說法是倒果為因。他又形容，留任是「留住手上小小的武器」，若政府無意解開社會撕裂，民主派任何時間都可以有新的部署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/531236/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BB-%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%A5-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E7%95%99%E4%BB%BB%E9%BB%98%E8%AA%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B-%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E6%96%A5%E5%80%92%E6%9E%9C%E7%82%BA%E5%9B%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F531236%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2581%25A5-%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E9%25BB%2598%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258A%259B-%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%2596%25A5%25E5%2580%2592%25E6%259E%259C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%259B%25A0&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=3a677598\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/531236/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BB-%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%A5-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E7%95%99%E4%BB%BB%E9%BB%98%E8%AA%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B-%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E6%96%A5%E5%80%92%E6%9E%9C%E7%82%BA%E5%9B%A0</a>"},{"pid":"033cda56be1f029bc91c5caeacc0d5f025bd56cc","tid":2227673,"uid":120837,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T03:43:27.000Z